        {
            "title": "日本沒有直接評論川普是否要求不要在台灣問題上挑釁中國的提問",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 對於有關美國總統唐納德·川普是否建議日本首相高市早苗避免在台灣問題上激怒中國的提問，日本政府首席發言人沒有直接回答。此前有報導稱雙方曾進行過此類交流。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我無法就外交政策相關的交流作進一步評論。」日本內閣官房長官木原稔周四在例行記者會上被問及該報導是否屬實，他表示，在本周川普與高市的通話中，「兩位領導人確認了美日之間的密切合作」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》此前報導稱，川普在通話中建議高市不要在台灣主權問題上挑釁北京。報導引述了未具名日本官員和一位了解通話情況的美國人。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-61e29c92-a3fe-3065-be54-3dd94bef8723-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：日本首相高市早苗稱之前談及台灣問題時並未打算提及任何細節</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan Avoids Comment on Whether Trump Asked Not to Provoke China</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F-030309022.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 11:50:58",
